# Pulse

A lightweight monitoring platform built from scratch.

## Components

- C++ metrics agent
- Go REST API
- SQLite storage
- React dashboard

## Features

- Live CPU/RAM graphs
- Historical metrics
- Multi-host support
- REST API

## Roadmap

- [x] SQLite storage
- [x] React dashboard
- [ ] Time range selector
- [ ] Process monitoring
- [ ] Docker deployment
